# Logbook domain (UI)

## Flight form — editable fields

`date`, `pilot`, `copilot`, `glider`, `registration`, `departure_place`, `launch_time`, `landing_time`, `arrival_place`, `launch_type`, `landings`, `is_instructor`, `remarks`

**Read-only** (show after save, from API): `flight_time`, `pic_time`, `dual_time`, `instructor_time`, `row_number`

## Validation (mirror backend)

- `date`: ISO `YYYY-MM-DD` (display may follow Settings `date_format`)
- `launch_time`, `landing_time`: `HH:MM`
- `landings`: integer ≥ 0
- `launch_type`: free text (suggest Aerotow, Winch but allow custom)

## Settings affect UX

- `date_format`, `sort_direction`, `pilot_name`, `is_instructor` — from `GET /api/settings`
- `zebra_color`, `header_color` — read-only, optional theming

## Summary / medical

- Summary: 7 optional date fields (ISO in API)
- Medical: exactly **3 entries** on PATCH (`start_date`, `medical_type`, `expiry_date`)

## Statistics dashboard

`GET /api/statistics` — totals, `flights_by_glider`, `flights_by_launch_type`, `recent_activity` (max 10).

## Empty states

- Not logged in → login
- No logbook → connect flow (Google Drive Picker)
- No flights → empty list, not an error
